Class AltoClefTickChart

java.lang.Object
adris.altoclef.ui.AltoClefTickChart
public class AltoClefTickChart extends Object
displays a chart indicating how much of the tick time is taken up by altoclef (very similar to Minecrafts `TickChart`)
